 Tuệ tôn giả kỳ 1 - 寄普慧尊者其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/author-YFBCcaKGsPA7uILcS-B8_Q">Trần Anh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/Nh%C6%B0-m%E1%BB%99ng-l%E1%BB%87nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Như mộng lệnh kỳ 2 - 如夢令其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%E1%BA%A3o-Am/S%C6%A1n-pha-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-6FKE2K_eX4toOZtBDjmyJg">Sơn pha dương kỳ 1 - 山坡羊其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%E1%BA%A3o-Am/author-BI-5R4NCDfEksvoGyyrUTg">Trần Thảo Am</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C3%A1i-vi-6/poem-ivW_yivdLYHr5btKQsjpYA">Thái vi 6 - 采薇 6</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Xu%C3%A2n-th%C3%A0nh-du-ngo%E1%BA%A1n/poem-HkjeyB7wwwOBavgBZHHXuQ">Xuân thành du ngoạn - 春城遊玩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
